PUBLIC DOMAIN NOTICE
===============================================================================

"earth.library" is freeware, not shareware. There is no fee.

On the other hand, there are advantages to "registering". Just send a
blank disc and a stamped self-addressed envelope (enclose an
international reply coupon if writing from outside the UK) and we will
fill your disc full of goodies (ie latest releases of EarthSoft products)
and post it back to you. If you forget the stamped envelope (or
international reply coupon) then we shall keep your disc - you have been
warned.

"earth.library" was written by Arcane Jill.
Copyright 1992, EarthSoft.

